main event: Several witnesses observed multiple unidentified flying objects over Lake Carmel, New York, on 27 July 1966.
interesting points: Observers noted varied colors in the dome-like surfaces of the objects, One object produced a high-pitched sound, The objects vanished instantly one at a time, Sightings occurred alongside identified aircraft in the area, Witnesses reported seeing as many as six objects simultaneously at times.
sighted object: several unidentified flying objects emitting varied colors of light
witness description: Civilian witnesses, including local residents and family members.
